dogs.name: Vanilla
dogs.description: Vanilla is a merry and busy little dog. Profuse and glamorous,  she is an intelligent dog who loves her family

dogs.name: Angus
dogs.description: Solid, muscular and robust, Angus is an athletic dog who loves to help his family on the farm. Playful and loyal, Angus is a great companion

dogs.name: Lassie
dogs.description: Loyal and intelligent, Lassie is a wonderful companion. Lassies is an active, friendly, loving dog, who is always wagging his tail

dogs.name: Dottie
dogs.description: Dottie is friendly and outgoing. She is dedicated and loyal, enjoys company and is always clowning about

dogs.name: Bob
dogs.description: Bob is tenacious and courageous, but also very goofy. He is highly affectionate and kind, and loves to nap and eat

dogs.name: Coco
dogs.description: Coco is affectionate and intelligent, energetic and full of fun
